Commentary Text: Jadeja to Stoinis, out Bowled!! Cleaned em up!! Stoinis is shell-shocked. Sharp turn again as this was a full delivery that pitches outside leg stump, spins away and crashes onto the top of off. Stoinis totally beaten. He is literally asking was I bowled from that spot? How? He is still staring in disbelief. Jaddu is turning the game once again... Just one of those nothing-you-could-do balls. Stoinis b Jadeja 6(4) [4s-1]

Commentary Text: Theekshana to Krunal Pandya, out Caught by Rahane!! Two in two!! Krunal Pandya is out for a duck on captaincy debut. This was flat and just kept leaving the batter. Krunal had a poke and the ball flies off the edge towards Rahane at first slip. It came quick and it was a really sharp, low take from Jinks. A proper Test match slip catch that we've seen him take so often in whites, probably the first time in a yellow CSK jersey. Maheesh Theekshana on a hat-trick. Krunal Pandya c Rahane b Theekshana 0(1)

Commentary Text: Moeen Ali to Mayers, out Caught by Gaikwad!! Moeen has Mayers' number once again!! It wasn't necessary for the southpaw to attack the unfavourable match-up. But he couldn't resist as Moeen gave the ball some flight. Mayers charged out for a big slog, the bat turns as he plays the shot and Gaikwad at long-off wasn't going to make a mistake with this one. CSK strike early... Mayers c Gaikwad b Moeen Ali 14(17) [4s-2]
